spec_data.Name: mldonkey-server
spec_data.Description:
Contains init and configs to launch mldonkey as a service.

NOTE: by default incoming dir is located in /var/lib/mldonkey/incoming
and temp dir in /var/lib/cache/mldonkey. Mlondkey is launched
with the mldonkey user (created after installation).

NOTE: If you are using a password for your mldonkey, you need to specify
it in your /etc/sysconfig/mldonkey, because mldonkey now stores
it encrypted.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 08 Aug 2017 10:39:25 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Enables mldonkey as a system daemon
